{"tid":100002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"京城民眾狂放炮仗煙花 空氣污染極速惡化","createTime":"2017-01-29T15:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T10:17:43.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9ce6e91e163de7eb08c91da7573f6db836637a3","tid":100002,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:45:18.000Z","msg":"京津照放炮仗　污染爆錶 <br />\n另一方面，今年春節假期留在國內的民眾，則要繼續忍受霧霾之苦。包括北京等國內城市，近日均對市民燃放煙花爆竹祭出嚴控姿態，惟民眾仍堅持「爆竹一聲除舊歲」。其中京津冀大批民眾前晚開始燃放炮仗，令區域PM2.5懸浮粒子濃度急升。 <br />\n官方公佈北京的空氣質量指數（AQI）在昨凌晨1時至5時超過500，達嚴重污染的「爆錶」水平，若用美國標準更曾升至724的峯值，至昨早天明時才有所改善。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170129/small/29ck2p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170129%2Fsmall%2F29ck2p.jpg&h=57b1538f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170129/19912408?_ga=1.44514214.301274154.1485697500%3Cbr%20/%3E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170129%2F19912408%3F_ga%3D1.44514214.301274154.1485697500%253Cbr%2520%2F%253E&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=97e26c23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170129%2F19912408%3F_ga%3D1.44514214.301274154.1485697500%253Cbr%2520%2F%253E&h=45a5876a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170129/19912408?_ga=1.44514214.301274154.1485697500%3Cbr%20/%3E</a>"},{"pid":"f7ff9f42a04d05ec996330907a2bfc445819f458","tid":100002,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:56:17.000Z","msg":"放假冇毒霧吸唔係好慣"},{"pid":"d4b49a4719477dea835f490d8a026d33116889a3","tid":100002,"uid":10707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T04:51:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>京津照放炮仗　污染爆錶 <br />\n另一方面，今年春節假期留在國內的民眾，則要繼續忍受霧霾之苦。包